                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6359" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CPGN-0197</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8168 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">不破不立：惠博普“油水互助”的混改之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">There&#39;s no Making Without Breaking.: Huibopu&#39;s &quot;oil and Water Mutual assistance&quot; Mixed Reform Road</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">程文莉，余霜，杨佳莉，艾多为</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华油惠博普科技股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">惠博普；民企混改；体制机制改革；控制权</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> Huibopu；mixed reform of private enterprises；reform of institutional mechanisms；control</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了民营企业惠博普的混改历程。惠博普以民营资本起步进入油服行业，2019年通过引进战略投资者的方式实现与国资股权的混合。“混”股权完成后，惠博普进行了董事会换届选举以及管理调整等体制机制改革，混改当年在战略和业绩方面成果初显，在疫情的影响下也充分体现民企混改发挥的资源效应。本案例以“混”与“改”为主线，通过对双方混改的动因、机制改革、控制权模式及产生的效应等内容进行分析，旨在引导学生运用公司治理相关理论分析“逆向混改”决策，理解其中不破不立的混改逻辑，思考治理模式对治理水平和保障整体并购绩效的推动作用，也为有意向引入国资的民企在混改路径等方面提供借鉴与参考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes the mixed reform process of the private enterprise Huibopu. Huibopu started into the oil service industry with private capital, and in 2019, it achieved a mix with state-owned equity by introducing strategic investors. After the completion of the &quot;mixed&quot; equity, Huibopu carried out institutional reforms such as the election of the board of directors and management adjustments, and the results of the mixed reform in terms of strategy and performance in that year began to appear, and the resource effect of the mixed reform of private enterprises was fully reflected under the influence of the epidemic. Taking &quot;mixing&quot; and &quot;reform&quot; as the main line, this case analyzes the motives, mechanism reform, control mode and effects of the mixed reform of both sides, etc., aims to guide students to use the relevant theories of corporate governance to analyze the decision of &quot;reverse mixed reform&quot;, understand the logic of mixed reform that is not broken, think about the role of the governance model in promoting the governance level and ensuring the overall M&amp;A performance, and also provide reference and reference for private enterprises that intend to introduce state-owned assets in the mixed reform path.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司治理》、《公司财务》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">混合所有制；混改动因；政治关联理论；战略联盟理论；混改路径:引入战略投资者；现代产权和公司治理理论；公司控制权模式:创始人控制；股东控制；混改效应:治理效应(股权集中度、董事会领导结构)；资源效应</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-07</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
